
                            <%inherit file="perspective_template.mako"/>
                            <p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">加拿大公司员工福利计划<u>一般都只提供给</u></span><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">full-time</span></u><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">员工，或者是某些特定职业的工会的成员</span></u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">。因为公司的保险是单独和保险公司制定的，所以每个公司的方案内容和报销的比例，条件都不一样。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">在这里，以为我朋友公司提供保险方案为例，帮大家解析一下，内容很多，这篇我们先讲讲</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;"> Health&amp;Dental </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">方面的。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">介绍具体</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">Helath</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">和</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;"> Dental</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">内容之前，<strong><span style="font-family: SimSun;">首先一定要记住公司保险计划的六个关键信息：</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #888888; background: white;">TIPS: </span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: DengXian; color: #888888; background: white;">一定不能忽略的六个关键信</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: SimSun; color: #888888; background: white;">息</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong>1. Effective date/Enrolment period </strong><strong><span style="font-family: SimSun;">有</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">效期和注册期</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 18.7pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">每年的计划生效之前，公司都会给你时间做修改，比如是否带上配偶，是否增加保障额度。如果你错过了这段时间不选择，公司默认你当年选择设定好的标准计划。<u>除非员工的</u></span><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">life events</span></u><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">发生改变，例如（结婚，离婚，孩子刚刚出生等等）</span></u></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong>2. Policy number</strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">保单号码</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">保单号，是提交索赔申请的重要信息之一。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong>3. Phone number</strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">客服电话</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">有什么疑问，可以直接联系客服，方便和保险公司沟通。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong>4. How to claim&nbsp;</strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">如何索赔？需要准备哪些材料</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: SimSun;">？</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">比如药物相关的费用，可以直接刷保险公司给的</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&ldquo;</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">医疗卡</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&rdquo;</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">，但是牙齿或者针灸按摩类的费用可能需要自己先垫付，之后提交付款收据，和医生诊断书，索赔表，经过保险公司审核，才能收到赔偿金。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong>5. Claim Period&nbsp;</strong><strong><span style="font-family: SimSun;">索赔期</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 7.5pt; text-indent: 24pt; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">一定要弄清楚，在什么时间内提交索赔是有效的。比如有的保险计划规定，</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">90</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">天内必须提交索赔申请，如果超出</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">90</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">天，就无法理赔。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong>6. Update beneficiary information&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">及时更新受益人信息</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">大部分公司都会提供<u>基础保额的人寿险。</u>如果不填写受益人名字，赔偿金会算作员工遗产的一部分，不会直接以支票形式给到指定受益人手中。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #888888; background: white;">Health &amp; Dental Benefits</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: SimSun; color: #888888; background: white;">篇</span></strong></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">接下来我们就看看具体有哪些福利吧</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm;" type="disc">
<li style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Prescription Drugs</span></strong></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">处方药</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm;" type="disc">
<li style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Medical Services &amp; Equipment</span></strong></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">医疗服务和器械</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;"> </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">比如陆地救护车或者空中救援，助步器，血压测量仪，轮椅等等</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm;" type="disc">
<li style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Hospital</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">（</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">home province</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">）</span></strong></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">主要是报销住院期间半私人病房</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">Semiprivate room</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">的费用。</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: red;">而不是报销住院的医疗费用！！！这点切记啊！！很多人误以为公司的保险还能报销入院治疗费用！！</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm;" type="disc">
<li style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Emergency travel assistance</span></strong></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">去外省或者境外旅游，发生的紧急医疗费用，一定要注意它承包的时间，</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: red;">一般只有</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: red;">30-180</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: red;">天，而且不包含旅游之前已经存在的病症。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm;" type="disc">
<li style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Paramedical services</span></strong></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">比如针灸师，按摩师，心理咨询师，脊椎按摩师等等</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm;" type="disc">
<li style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Vision</span></strong></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">每两年或者一年一次</span></u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">的视力检查，配眼镜的费用</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul style="margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0cm;" type="disc">
<li style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-right: 0cm; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Dental</span></strong></li>
</ul>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; background: white; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">牙齿方面的医疗费用主要来自</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">Preventive</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">，</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">Restorative</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">和</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;"> Orthodontics</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">这三个方面。<u>一般公司的保险都可以报销</u></span><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">preventive</span></u><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">预防型的费用，比如洗牙，牙齿</span></u><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">X</span></u><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">光检测。</span></u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">但是涉及补牙，拔牙方面，很多公司报销的比例比较低，甚至是没有这方面的保障。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><img src="../static/article_images/image_45719716021618083764809.png" width="595" height="430" /></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">问：<u>我有公司健康保险，还要申请省健康卡吗？</u></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">答：<strong><span style="font-family: SimSun;">当然要！</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">公司的保险是<span style="color: red;">不包括的在诊所或者医院治疗的费用的！没有健康卡期间，一定购买单独的医疗保险</span>。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">问：<u>加拿大有免费的医疗卡，和公司医疗保险会有冲突吗？</u></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">答：<strong><span style="font-family: SimSun;">不会</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">省医疗卡作为第一支付方（处方药，牙齿，视力都不包的），额外的费用再通过公司保险报销。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">问：<u>如果我带上配偶和孩子，保费会增加吗？</u></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">答：<strong><span style="font-family: SimSun;">会的</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">而且每年的费用都有可能会调整（一般都是上涨）</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">问：<u>如果我主动辞职，被辞退了，或者</u></span><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">65</span></u><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">岁退休了，这些福利计划还能保留吗？</span></u></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">答：<strong><span style="font-family: SimSun;">不能</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">所有费用都必须自己承担，所以要提前准备个人的健康险。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">问：<u>如果我入职之前就有一些健康问题，比如牙齿已经有问题了，还能报销吗？</u></span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">答：<strong><span style="font-family: SimSun;">可以的</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">一般公司提供的默认的基础方案，是不需要员工填写医疗问卷的。（个人觉得这项这个真的太人性了！）</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">问：<u>公司在</u></span><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">Health &amp; Dental</span></u><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">方面的保险，有等待期吗？</span></u></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">答：<strong><span style="font-family: SimSun;">一般是没有的</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">过了公司</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">3</span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">个月的实习期，就能立刻生效。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">问：<u>什么是</u></span><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">deductible amount</span></u><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">？</span></u></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">答：<strong><span style="font-family: SimSun;">垫底费</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-size: 11.5pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun;">就是自己必须先垫付的部分，剩下的按比例报销。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="color: black;">最后，</span><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">大部分的加拿大的员工健康保险，是能承包已有健康问题员工，而且能立刻生效，</span></u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">帮助了有已经有健康问题的家庭，承担了很多医疗费用。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">即使现在年轻，健康，也要花些时间去了解，及时根据家庭状况做调整。<u>拔颗牙，买个轮椅</u></span><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;"> </span></u><u><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">如果没有保险的话，说不定半个月工资就没有了。</span></u></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">如果职业变动，提前准备好个人健康险，避免出现空档期。</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #333333;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 13.0pt; font-family: SimSun; color: #333333;">谁能知道意外什么时候发生呢？</span></strong></p>